## 📖 Overview

CampusBuddy is a next-generation student community platform designed to become the **digital operating system of every college campus**.

College life is much more than attending classes. Students constantly search for internships, hackathons, club recruitments, events, study groups, mentors, teammates, and opportunities—but this information is scattered across WhatsApp groups, Telegram channels, Instagram pages, Discord servers, notice boards, and word of mouth.

CampusBuddy solves this problem by providing **one centralized platform** where students can communicate, collaborate, discover opportunities, participate in discussions, and build meaningful campus connections.

Whether you're a freshman looking for guidance, a senior preparing for placements, a club organizing events, or a student searching for teammates—CampusBuddy brings everyone together.

